  "summary": "CVE-2023-25659 affecting package tensorflow for versions less than 2.11.1-1",
  "details": "TensorFlow is an open source platform for machine learning. Prior to versions 2.12.0 and 2.11.1, if the parameter `indices` for `DynamicStitch` does not match the shape of the parameter `data`, it can trigger an stack OOB read. A fix is included in TensorFlow version 2.12.0 and version 2.11.1.\n",
